'''戈迪·豪國際大橋'''（{{lang-en|Gordie Howe International Bridge}}；{{lang-fr|Pont International Gordie-Howe}}）是一條擬建連接[[美國|美國]]與[[加拿大|加拿大]]的跨國橋樑，規劃中跨越[[底特律河|底特律河]]連接美國[[密芝根州|密芝根州]][[底特律|底特律]]和加拿大[[安大略省|安大略省]][[溫莎_(安大略省)|溫莎]]。這座橋樑在美國端將與[[75號州際公路|75號州際公路]]交接，在加拿大端則將會駁上[[安大略401號省道|安大略401號省道]]，為來往兩地的車流提供全程達至[[高速公路|高速公路]]資格的途徑<ref>{{cite web |title=Parkway Map |author=Detroit River International Crossing Study Team |publisher=URS Corporation |date=2008-05-01 |url=http://www.weparkway.ca/pdfs/Prelim_Parkway-Rendered_June09(608x2250)2.pdf |accessdate=2010-02-25 |format=PDF |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110706213130/http://www.weparkway.ca/pdfs/Prelim_Parkway-Rendered_June09(608x2250)2.pdf |archive-date=2011-07-06 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。大橋的工程於2018年展開<ref name=ws1st2020/><ref name="WDBA150925"/>，預計2024年通車<ref name=wsland/><ref name="WDBA150514"/>。

==歷史==
[[底特律-溫莎地區|底特律-溫莎地區]]之内的邊檢口岸為美加兩國之間的主要貿易通道，單在2012年便有250萬架次的貨車在此過境，貿易額高達1056億加元，佔美加之間以貨車承載的貿易額約31%<ref name="TC140228">{{cite web |title=Status Report on Transformational and Major Crown Projects |publisher=[[加拿大交通部|加拿大交通部]] |date=2014-02-28 |url=https://www.tc.gc.ca/eng/corporate-services/planning-rpp-2014-2015-1112.html |accessdate=2016-09-19 |archive-date=2020-02-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200219150108/https://www.tc.gc.ca/eng/corporate-services/planning-rpp-2014-2015-1112.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。然而，跨越[[底特律河|底特律河]]連接[[底特律|底特律]]和[[溫莎_(安大略省)|溫莎]]兩市的兩個主要車流渡口[[大使橋|大使橋]]和[[底特律-溫莎隧道|底特律-溫莎隧道]]皆不與[[南安大略|南安大略]]以至[[魁北克市-溫莎走廊|魁北克市-溫莎走廊]]上的主要高速公路[[安大略401號省道|安大略401號省道]]接駁；駕駛人士需透過溫莎市内的非高速公路規格街道前往該兩個渡口。此外，逾99%在此過境的貨車取道已有超過80年歷史的大使橋<ref name="TC140228"/>，但該橋來回方向各得兩條行車線，而來往兩市的車流預計從2016年的每日18500架次上升至2025年的每日26500架次<ref name="MDOT report">{{cite news |first=Jonathan |last=Oosting |url=http://www.mlive.com/news/detroit/index.ssf/2010/06/mdot_report_detroit_river_inte.html |title=MDOT Report: Detroit River International Crossing |work=MLive |location=Detroit |publisher=Booth Newspapers |date=June 17, 2010 |accessdate=October 12, 2010 |archive-date=2016-03-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304052357/http://www.mlive.com/news/detroit/index.ssf/2010/06/mdot_report_detroit_river_inte.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>，該橋將難以應付日益增長的車流。

有見及此，加美兩地政府於2004年展開'''底特律河國際渡口'''項目（{{lang|en|Detroit River International Crossing}}），研究在當地設置第三個渡口。項目[[環境評估|環境評估]]程序於2005年2月展開，審視15個項目選項<ref name="TC140228"/>。[[加拿大交通部|加拿大交通部]]於2008年獲准在溫莎市就徵地興建大橋落腳點和加拿大邊檢關卡展開磋商，而項目環評則於2009年末完成<ref name="TC140228"/>。安大略省政府則從2011年8月起將401號公路西延，以便日後與大橋接駁<ref name="TC140228"/>。

密芝根州參議院的經濟發展委員會於2011年10月否決方案，為項目增添變數<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.huffingtonpost.ca/2011/10/21/canada-us-trade-windsor-detroit-bridge_n_1023927.html |title=Canada–U.S. Trade: Michigan Senate Committee Kills New Border Crossing |work=[[Huffington_Post|Huffington Post]] |first=Daniel |last=Tencer |date=November 21, 2011 |accessdate=June 15, 2012 |archive-date=2021-03-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210313161838/https://www.huffingtonpost.ca/2011/10/21/canada-us-trade-windsor-detroit-bridge_n_1023927.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。然而，加拿大聯邦政府和密芝根州政府則於2012年6月達成協議，以[[公私合作伙伴關係|公私合作伙伴關係]]（P3）模式進行項目，當中加方同意全數支付興建大橋、在密芝根州徵地和興建交流道通往[[75號州際公路|75號州際公路]]的費用。加方將向從溫莎通往底特律的車流收取過橋費彌補項目開支，相反方向車流則不用繳費<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.cbc.ca/news/canada/windsor/story/2012/06/14/wdr-prime-minister-bridge-windsor-detroit.html |title=$1B Windsor–Detroit Bridge Deal Struck |publisher=[[Canadian_Broadcasting_Corporation|CBC News]] |date=June 15, 2012 |accessdate=June 15, 2012 |archive-date=2013-08-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130823094942/http://www.cbc.ca/news/canada/windsor/story/2012/06/14/wdr-prime-minister-bridge-windsor-detroit.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。雙方亦根據該協議在同年10月成立溫莎-底特律大橋管理局（{{lang|en|Windsor-Detroit Bridge Authority}}）；該機構負責管理大橋的設計、建造、營運和維修程序，以及釐定大橋的收費架構<ref name="WDBA140630">{{cite web |url=https://www.wdbridge.com/en/appointments-to-the-international-authority-and-the-windsor-detroit-bridge-authority |title=Appointments to the International Authority and the Windsor-Detroit Bridge Authority |publisher=溫莎-底特律大橋管理局 |date=2014-06-30 |accessdate=2016-09-20 |archive-date=2018-02-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180213054814/https://www.wdbridge.com/en/appointments-to-the-international-authority-and-the-windsor-detroit-bridge-authority |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

[[美國國務院|美國國務院]]和奧巴馬政府於2013年4月向密芝根州政府發出項目許可證<ref>{{cite news |first=Dave |last=Battagello |date=April 12, 2013 |title=Michigan Governor Snyder Confirms Permit for DRIC Approved |url=http://blogs.windsorstar.com/2013/04/12/michigan-governor-snyder-confirms-permit-for-dric-approved/ |work=The Windsor Star |accessdate=April 12, 2013 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131114092542/http://blogs.windsorstar.com/2013/04/12/michigan-governor-snyder-confirms-permit-for-dric-approved/ |archive-date=2013-11-14 |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |title=New Windsor-Detroit bridge gets Obama's OK |url=http://www.cbc.ca/news/canada/windsor/story/2013/04/12/wdr-dric-presidential-permit-windsor-detroit-rick-snyder-michigan.html |publisher=CBC News |date=April 12, 2013 |accessdate=April 12, 2013 |archive-date=2013-08-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130828130920/http://www.cbc.ca/news/canada/windsor/story/2013/04/12/wdr-dric-presidential-permit-windsor-detroit-rick-snyder-michigan.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name=permit>{{cite press release |author=Office of the Spokesperson |date=April 12, 2013 |title=Issuance of Presidential Permit for New International Trade Crossing |url=http://www.state.gov/r/pa/prs/ps/2013/04/207424.htm |publisher=[[United_States_Department_of_State|United States Department of State]] |id=2013/0402 |accessdate=April 12, 2013 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161111135921/http://www.state.gov/r/pa/prs/ps/2013/04/207424.htm/ |archive-date=2016-11-11 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>，而加拿大聯邦政府則於同年5月撥款2500萬加元，以備在密芝根州徵地<ref name="wsland" />。負責管理大橋P3協議的國際管理局（{{lang|en|International Authority}}）委員名單則於2014年6月公佈，加拿大和密芝根州各有三名代表<ref name="WDBA140630"/><ref>{{cite web|url=http://blogs.windsorstar.com/news/new-dric-bridge-executive-team-loaded-with-financial-expertise |title=DRIC bridge executive teams loaded with financial expertise, but nobody local |work=Windsor Star |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150702192758/http://blogs.windsorstar.com/news/new-dric-bridge-executive-team-loaded-with-financial-expertise |archivedate=2015-07-02 }}</ref>。加拿大交通部長雷特（{{lang|en|Lisa Raitt}}）於2015年2月宣佈加方將斥資興建大橋在美國端的邊檢關卡<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.cbc.ca/news/canada/windsor/250m-u-s-customs-plaza-to-be-paid-for-by-canada-1.2962166|title=$250M U.S. customs plaza to be paid for by Canada|work=CBC News|accessdate=May 14, 2015|archive-date=2015-02-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150224003115/http://www.cbc.ca/news/canada/windsor/250m-u-s-customs-plaza-to-be-paid-for-by-canada-1.2962166|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=freep-customsdeal>{{cite news|title=Deal for new customs plaza in Detroit announced|url=http://www.freep.com/story/news/local/2015/02/18/bridge-plaza-deal/23606333/|accessdate=14 May 2015|work=Detroit Free Press|publisher=Gannett Company|date=February 18, 2015|archive-date=2020-12-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201201193344/https://www.freep.com/story/news/local/2015/02/18/bridge-plaza-deal/23606333/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。大橋管理局從2015年7月開始尋求項目私營伙伴<ref name="WDBA150720">{{cite web |url=https://www.wdbridge.com/en/windsor-detroit-bridge-authority-announces-launch-of-the-procurement-process-for-the-gordie-howe-international-bridge |title=Windsor-Detroit Bridge Authority announces launch of the procurement process for the Gordie Howe International Bridge |publisher=溫莎-底特律大橋管理局 |date=2015-07-20 |accessdate=2016-09-20 |archive-date=2017-01-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170114173443/https://www.wdbridge.com/en/windsor-detroit-bridge-authority-announces-launch-of-the-procurement-process-for-the-gordie-howe-international-bridge |dead-url=no }}</ref>，並於同年8月將總值5900萬加元的加拿大邊檢關卡工地平整工程合約批予安大略的阿米科基建公司（{{lang|en|Amico Infrastructure}}）<ref name="WDBA150925">{{cite web |url=https://www.wdbridge.com/en/early-works |title=Early Works – An Overview |publisher=溫莎-底特律大橋管理局 |date=2015-09-25 |accessdate=2016-09-20 |archive-date=2017-03-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170330220743/https://www.wdbridge.com/en/early-works |dead-url=no }}</ref>。當局則於2016年1月宣佈三間財團入圍競逐項目私營伙伴<ref name="WDBA160120">{{cite web |url=https://www.wdbridge.com/en/wdba-announces-short-listed-respondents-for-gordie-howe-international-bridge |title=WDBA Announces Short-Listed Respondents for Gordie Howe International Bridge |publisher=溫莎-底特律大橋管理局 |date=2016-01-20 |accessdate=2016-09-20 |archive-date=2017-11-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171107021812/https://www.wdbridge.com/en/wdba-announces-short-listed-respondents-for-gordie-howe-international-bridge |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

==命名==
此項目早期稱為'''底特律河國際渡口'''（{{lang|en|Detroit River International Crossing}}），然而有見該名稱的簡寫「DRIC」與[[大使橋|大使橋]]營運機構底特律國際大橋公司（{{lang|en|Detroit International Bridge Company}}）的簡寫「DIBC」相近<ref name=mlive/>，項目在密芝根州内的名稱改為'''新國際貿易渡口'''（{{lang|en|New International Trade Crossing}}）以免混淆<ref name="WDBA140630"/>。

安大略貨車協會主席布拉德利（{{lang|en|David Bradley}}）於2010年提出以長年效力[[國家冰球聯盟|國家冰球聯盟]][[底特律紅翼隊|底特律紅翼隊]]的加拿大職業冰球員[[戈迪·豪|戈迪·豪]]來命名這座橋樑，並獲得多名加拿大政客和戈迪·豪的兒子馬提（{{lang|en|Marty Howe}}）支持<ref name=mlive>{{cite news |last=Wattrick |first=Jeff |title=Forget the DRIC, How About the Gordie Howe International Bridge? |url=http://www.mlive.com/news/detroit/index.ssf/2011/02/forget_the_dric_how_about_the.html |work=MLive |location=Detroit |publisher=Booth Newspapers |date=February 3, 2011 |accessdate=February 5, 2011 |archive-date=2018-06-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180618203835/http://www.mlive.com/news/detroit/index.ssf/2011/02/forget_the_dric_how_about_the.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="mw-howe">{{cite news |last=Noble |first=Chris |url=http://blogs.marketwatch.com/canada/2011/02/08/gordie-howe-bridge-floated-as-new-spans-name/ |title=Gordie Howe Bridge Floated as New Span's Name |work=MarketWatch |date=February 8, 2011 |accessdate=November 2, 2012 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160610103553/http://blogs.marketwatch.com/canada/2011/02/08/gordie-howe-bridge-floated-as-new-spans-name/ |archive-date=2016-06-10 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。2015年5月14日，時任[[加拿大總理|加拿大總理]][[史提芬·哈珀|哈珀]]宣佈將大橋命名為戈迪·豪國際大橋；在席包括密芝根州州長[[里克·斯奈德|斯奈德]]和戈迪·豪家人<ref name="WDBA150514"/><ref name=cbc-gordiehowebridge>{{cite news|title=Gordie Howe International Bridge to connect Windsor and Detroit|url=http://www.cbc.ca/news/canada/windsor/gordie-howe-international-bridge-to-connect-windsor-and-detroit-1.3074243|accessdate=May 14, 2015|publisher=CBC News|date=May 14, 2015|archive-date=2021-02-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210213162159/https://www.cbc.ca/news/canada/windsor/gordie-howe-international-bridge-to-connect-windsor-and-detroit-1.3074243|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

